{"tid":552714,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[北海道緊急求教] 有無巴打去過釧路？","createTime":"2018-02-06T19:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T08:14:39.000Z","uid":50878,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c02ab8d15f30db337fff25f81ec9664ca78bfd","tid":552714,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:09:33.000Z","msg":"想問下朝早一個景點<br />\n下午要準時7pm就搭車番札幌<br />\n<br />\n有咩景點係趕得切？ 定還是一定要留係釧路一晚先安全d? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09817f5aafdf1d5077e443e469be59d2ccaf3ced","tid":552714,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:19:15.000Z","msg":"即係即日來回！？"},{"pid":"e746b9da05c8f7a037dc044d8f835ef472591c02","tid":552714,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09817f5aafdf1d5077e443e469be59d2ccaf3ced","tid":552714,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:19:15.000Z","msg":"即係即日來回！？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:50:48.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係前一晚好夜去釧路訓，第二朝起身走景點，跟住番札幌<br />\n<br />\n因為唔想住釧路兩晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗緊坐冬之濕原號來回，3:40pm 番到釧路就比較多時間<br />\n<br />\n其他道東三湖bus tour 或者自己搭巴士去鶴見台都應該搞到夜晚6,7點先番到釧路<br />\n<br />\n一miss 左札幌番車就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36017095df08c4836cdcd24957d529739358cf3","tid":552714,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"全部釧路市既景點咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a919697830afe71a